name: Baño de Luna
description: This art takes place in one of the poles of the planet YY, where the gravity of the ground pulls everything down and the 10 ~ 30 meters above the ground is nil, this was represented before in previous works like "Mechanic Mindset". Due to the fall of our character on the planet, this generated an imbalance that transformed both the upper and lower extremities into something defined by the local scientific authorities as a "Gravitational imbalance caused by external factors".
